容，无需 Markdown 知识！",[293,364,365,368],{},[296,366,367],{},"自动生成侧边导航","：根据内容结构自动生成导航。",[293,370,371,373],{},[296,372,158],{},"：包含内置搜索功能以便于内容发现。",[293,375,376,379],{},[296,377,378],{},"优化排版","：具有精致的排版以增强可读性。",[293,381,382,385],{},[296,383,384],{},"暗黑模式","：为用户偏好提供暗黑模式支持。",[293,387,388,391],{},[296,389,390],{},"广泛功能","：探索该主题以充分欣赏其能力。",[393,394,396],"template",{"v-slot:right":395},"",[397,398],"template-features",{":features":399},"[{\"label\":\"Nuxt 3\",\"content\":\"基于 Nuxt 3，性能与 SEO 表现优异。\"},{\"label\":\"Markdown\",\"content\":\"使用 Nuxt Content 支持的 MDC 编写页面内容。\"},{\"label\":\"Nuxt UI\",\"content\":\"提供大量完全可定制的组件。\"},{\"label\":\"TypeScript\",\"content\":\"完全类型化的开发体验。\"},{\"label\":\"Nuxt Studio\",\"content\":\"兼容 Nuxt Studio，实现快速更新与预览。\"},{\"label\":\"Search\",\"content\":\"由 Fuse.js 驱动的全文搜索模态框。\"}]",{"title":395,"searchDepth":401,"depth":401,"links":402},2,[403],{"id":285,"depth":401,"text":285},"main","docs","https://docus.dev","用 Markdown 编写美观的文档","md","/blog/docus.webp","nuxt-ui-pro","/templates/docus.webp",{"createdAt":413},"2023-11-15T17:41:03.087Z","docus",true,"nuxtlabs","/templates/docus",{"title":221,"description":407},"templates/docus","2PzHxih0gYUWagVMMYlnuakrdEsL9byvKgPhH6PtyxU",1751727801634]